com.observability.modeling.probe.descriptor.entities

Class Parameter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.observability.modeling.probe.descriptor.entities.Parameter
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Collect, Machine, Metric

    public abstract class Parameter
extends java.lang.Object
    The abstract class defines the attributes and methods needed to define parameters for any type of annotation.
    Any new annotation would need to extend this class.
    Currently, the following annotations are supported
  • @Metric
  • @Machine
  • @Collect
